TextEng: I want to ask you some questions.
I seek the cult that prolonged the Neverwinter plague.
Text: 저는 네버윈터 역병을 연장시킨 사교를 찾고 있습니다.

TextEng: What can you tell me about Charwood?
Text: 그을린숲에 대해 뭘 알려주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: Me looks for plague-pushing cult. They hurt Neverwinter.
Text: 나 역병 퍼뜨린 사교 찾아. 걔들 네버윈터 해쳤어.

TextEng: I was here before. Don't you remember?
Text: 저는 전에 여기 왔었는데요. 기억 안 나세요?

TextEng: Me here before now. You not remember?
Text: 나 전에 여기 왔어. 기억 안 나?

TextEng: Who are the important people in town?
Me ask something else about town.
Why did he take your child?
Where can I find this castle?
Text: 이 성을 어디서 찾을 수 있나요?

TextEng: Where can I find the Mayor?
Where me find this Mayor guy?
